comment.body:
@amoldavsky thanks for working on this! I'd love to see some docs about how to write new plugins and a general explanation of how this approach works.

I'd also want to be very sure that the "out of the box" functionality stays intact--as that's our primary use case and target audience: "a simple zero-configuration command-line http server"

I do like the idea of a more modular codebase and more configurable deployment options. Thanks for hacking on this idea!
